data.description: This beautiful home has lovely curb appeal with landscaped yard, large circular driveway and screened in entryway. as you enter you will take notice of the high vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, crown molding, and tile floors in common areas. The gourmet kitchen is designed to be the heart of the home that opens up to the great room. The kitchen is complete with granite countertops, tall cabinetry, a pantry, a long breakfast bar, and newer appliances and fixtures. Spectacular large sliding doors that open into the spacious lanai area from the great room. Perfect for entertaining. Huge master suite with additional office space with access to the lanai. Master bath offers his and her closets and sinks, large, tiled walk-in shower and big soaking tub. Formal dining room off the great room area. Laundry room has lots of cabinets and storage area. Split bedroom plan has 2 large bedrooms each with their own bathroom and walk in closets. 31 x 24 garage has 2 oversized bays and a golf cart garage area with door. The list goes on and on with the many upgrades this home has. Roof is new in the end of 2022. This home is well maintained and move in ready.
